  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- the story was, which I later find out, that as my mother didn't hear anything going on, she went out and the child ran in the street and she was caught in the last minute, brought in the last day when we were loaded to the train, whereas my mother then realize what's happened, went to the police and-- and volunteered.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The train was already gone, so she was left in Sadowa Wisznia, out of the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the train, I was with my grandmother, with my aunt, with my two sisters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember-- I told you the incident when I ask my grandmother, why you?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was always ailing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had a heart condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was very delicate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always, you know, everybody sort of worshiped her and she was a very delicate person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was in the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, God wishes like that to the last minute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we really didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- we passed Janowska.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We passed Lvov, because it was lit up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is where they deposited, they segregated the younger men who were still working age.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father and my aunt and my uncle were deposited-- I didn't know at that time-- They were somewhere else on the--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On Janowska.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the train, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were deposited in Janowska, and we were going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The slow train was moving very slowly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cattle train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I went to Washington museum and I saw the-- the museum.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to the train and I walked through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing conveys what-- you know, it's sanitized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It doesn't-- I know it performs a very good function, and I think it's important for the future generation.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
